title: The Definitive Power Ranking of Star Wars Games
description:
In today's episode, we're exploring the absolutely pristine history of Star Wars video games, and assigning each of them a grade in an EXTREMELY scientific and deliberate manner. It's a journey, y'all. 

Also discussed: Nobody Saves the World on Switch, Death's Gambit: Ashes of Vados, Fortnite, Rogue Legacy 2
author: thebestiesbizemail@gmail.com (Griffin McElroy, Justin McElroy, Russ Frushtick)
